SUMMARY:Lec60|Quantum algorithms for simulating the dynamics of open quantum systems|Chunhao Wang-Pennsylvania State University
LOCATION:https://tinyurl.com/gucs-zoom
DESCRIPTION:When a quantum system interacts with the environment\, it is no longer a unitary process\, and we refer to such systems as open quantum systems. In this lecture\, I will demonstrate the different behaviors between open and closed quantum systems. In addition\, I will present some recent developments in quantum algorithms for simulating such systems.
URL:https://qucs.info/lectures/60-quantum-algorithms-for-simulating-the-dynamics-of-open-quantum-systems
